Pre-Release 2.3.1

Base tag: v2.3.0
Diff source: current working tree against v2.3.0

Added
- Home page with progress dashboard, recommended next action, daily goal summary and quick access to achievements.
- First-run onboarding wizard for choosing language and layout before entering the app.
- Addons and mods system: content packs, JS-based mods, permissions, dependency checks, install/toggle/remove flows, addon template and Hardcore Mode example.
- New game systems: daily runs with deterministic seed, ghost run comparison, battle system v2, boss archetypes, item sets and extra diagnostics.

Changed
- Game mode progression, routes, events, items, HUD, result card and map flow were reworked around longer runs, boss encounters and richer reward decisions.
- Settings grew with built-in/custom presets, config import/export, interface density, accessibility toggles, keyboard placement controls and onboarding state.
- Navigation and UI were refreshed with new Home/Addons pages, updated sidebar/app routing, achievement surfaces, lessons/practice/test/settings polish and broad responsive styling updates.
- Main/preload/shared contracts were expanded to support addons, mods, presets, config IO and the new game state structures.

Fixed
- Persistence and Electron IPC were updated to correctly load/save addon, mod, theme and configuration data from the app data directory.
- Achievement evaluation now supports serialized conditions for core content and future addon/mod achievements.
